{"tid":2066790,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"日本職場經歷大改革 : 減低工時，謝絕OT","createTime":"2020-06-16T13:58:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-16T14:39:30.000Z","uid":353419,"like":7,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"4df52c499dc80783557daf0d7288f11954fff882","tid":2066790,"uid":353419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T13:58:32.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">勞動改革法案 : 最高工時， 加班時數上限，125%加班費 </span></strong><br />\n<br />\n幾年前，一宗過勞死的新聞轟動全國, 促成了勞動改革條例(働き方改革) , 自2018年, 法定勞動時間為每天8小時，每週40小時。每月加班時數以45小時為上限，需付125％加班費<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pKKY88b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpKKY88b.jpg&h=db94de0a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n日本TBS電視台的節目《News Caster》，訪問上班族對新條例的看法<br />\n<br />\n「我不需要（今年黃金周的）10天連休，反正也沒事做啊。」<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hNGQfTY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhNGQfTY.jpg&h=e9b468e7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n3X歲業務：「開會次數變成3分之1了」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VchLPeh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVchLPeh.jpg&h=67acea10&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n日本上班族:「不習慣放假」<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iVJCFmD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiVJCFmD.jpg&h=d8fbd161&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n日本上班族:「太早下班會被家人要求做家務」<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JNuN2AJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJNuN2AJ.jpg&h=a43e5bc0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n日本上班族:「不用工作很困擾」<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5w87h8J.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5w87h8J.jpg&h=41bc02d3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n,<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nSource : <a href=\"https://www.keguanjp.com/kgjp_jingji/kgjp_jj_etc/pt20190411060000.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.keguanjp.com%2Fkgjp_jingji%2Fkgjp_jj_etc%2Fpt20190411060000.html&d=St%2FdMm9ieZWtYGJEeV6aayEyVFbloTKGHdwbQdNTMZo%3D&h=dda67012\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.keguanjp.com/kgjp_jingji/kgjp_jj_etc/pt20190411060000.html</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.fnn.jp/articles/-/23508\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.fnn.jp%2Farticles%2F-%2F23508&d=St%2FdMm9ieZWtYGJEeV6aayEyVFbloTKGHdwbQdNTMZo%3D&h=99c7ea04\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.fnn.jp/articles/-/23508</a>    ..<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n..."},{"pid":"e3ae206782cd0ffa432d100072fe8a3fa96b01bb","tid":2066790,"uid":155818,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T13:59:21.000Z","msg":"最緊要夜晚唔洗應酬班老屎忽<br />\n一個一次都好夠, 日日真係<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"268e3204e5065183db99fd22a7e3a3a9b71c16f1","tid":2066790,"uid":72009,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T14:00:00.000Z","msg":"又咪去酒吧溝女"},{"pid":"f73ba9b50768a41001c2b2f88be4025abf144593","tid":2066790,"uid":161238,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T14:02:38.000Z","msg":"得把口姐 打左格仔又另一種講法"},{"pid":"edcaeaeda6794744dc586ad2400719b0578fd86d","tid":2066790,"uid":18001,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f73ba9b50768a41001c2b2f88be4025abf144593","tid":2066790,"uid":161238,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T14:02:38.000Z","msg":"得把口姐 打左格仔又另一種講法"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T14:04:56.000Z","msg":"可能好多人話支持但係Cut走咗"},{"pid":"23f09c5b985de0d6380d158eeac1bf687f830bd1","tid":2066790,"uid":353419,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"e3ae206782cd0ffa432d100072fe8a3fa96b01bb","tid":2066790,"uid":155818,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T13:59:21.000Z","msg":"最緊要夜晚唔洗應酬班老屎忽<br />\n一個一次都好夠, 日日真係<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T14:08:38.000Z","msg":"新立例好似禁止左放工應酬, 因為變相加班一種.